<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10May1939"><font color="red">10 May 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):  We think there is an error on page 34 &hellip; lines 11 and 12 from the foot have been transposed. Can you confirm this and we will alter this for a subsequent edition. </div>
